CircuitMaker
Circuitmaker is an extension of JPanel which allows for the user to draw schematics using the components supplied by the Components class in this project. uses mouse input to draw components with the selected component.
Component
Component is meant to be a data object for storing all possible component objects in a single arrayList inside of the class CircuitMaker.
